00:22:37,060 --> 00:22:38,720
 na zapadu sa neke industrije

328
00:22:38,720 --> 00:22:39,560
 ne mogu uopće,

329
00:22:39,560 --> 00:22:41,860
 ne mogu funkcionirati

330
00:22:41,860 --> 00:22:44,760
 bez komunikacije s njima,

331
00:22:44,760 --> 00:22:45,980
 to je ozbiljan problem

332
00:22:45,980 --> 00:22:47,040
 na svjetskoj razini,

333
00:22:47,040 --> 00:22:48,180
 tako da,

334
00:22:48,180 --> 00:22:49,420
 to su stvari koje,

