00:22:49,420 --> 00:22:49,860
 kažem,

336
00:22:49,860 --> 00:22:51,720
 i ovaj rat koji sad,

337
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:53,040
 koji Rusija vodi,

338
00:22:53,040 --> 00:22:54,780
 vi nećete moć,

339
00:22:54,780 --> 00:22:56,060
 kada ovaj rat završi,

340
00:22:56,060 --> 00:22:57,000
 vi morate svima sorađivati.

341
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:58,540
 Pa na, mi moraš pregovarati.

342
00:22:58,540 --> 00:22:59,300
 To je ogromna zemlja,

343
00:22:59,300 --> 00:23:00,460
 pazite, to je ogromna zemlja

344
00:23:00,460 --> 00:23:00,960
 koja ima,

